  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Passenger Ships transport migrants or tourists across t=
he
  galaxy. They pick up passengers from colonies and transport them either t=
o a new
  colony (for migration) or to a resort base (for tourism).<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-language:EN-GB;
  mso-no-proof:yes'>Passenger ships are privately owned and go about their
  business automatically. They are typically unarmed and lightly shielded.<=
o:p></o:p></span></p>
